token_info.name: Osawari! Incubus-kun!
token_info.description: An interactive NFT, collaboration of @fccview and @eitoasano. The collection was developed as a playable meme resurrecting the hype of early 20's flash games. Especially the branch called Eroge. We suggest to play the game in full-screen for the best experience. There is a brief nudity involved, parents strongly cautioned, some material may be inappropriate for children under 13.
